    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M Variable Differential Lock. This vehicle has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a complete VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The chassis utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry, currently fitted with Bilstein dampers for sharpened turn-in response. While the cabin and paintwork exhibit honest wear consistent with enthusiast use, the mechanical vitals are robust, providing the tactile feedback and linear power delivery synonymous with the M division\u2019s golden era.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
