    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available now is a meticulously maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 in Pearl White. This vehicle has been a reliable companion, benefiting from a full service history with oil changes every 5,000 miles. The parchment leather interior is clean and smoke-free, showing only light creasing on the driver's seat bolster. Under the hood, the engine and transmission operate smoothly with no known issues. The exterior maintains a high gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear plastic trim, consistent with daily driving. Equipped with a premium sound system and a set of tires with plenty of tread remaining, this SUV offers a perfect balance of luxury and dependability. It is a solid, honest vehicle ready for the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
