    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and mechanical integrity. This specimen features a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for reliability and performance. It represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-caliber automotive investment.",
      "price": 36500.0,
