    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014definitely well-loved and ready for a new home. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for many more adventures. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
