    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The high-revving power plant is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering linear torque to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. Mechanical integrity has been prioritized, with documented subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service already completed. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for exceptional lateral grip. While showing signs of spirited use consistent with its age, the chassis remains stiff and the throttle response is razor-sharp. A true driver\u2019s car for those who appreciate the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s high-RPM engineering.",
